item.title: About
item.description: Hello World! My name is Zach Blake and I am a software engineer from Washington state. Things are a bit on-again-off-again in terms of a formal education at the moment, but I’m hoping to turn that around in the near future so that I can finish pursuing a Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science. At the moment, I am working with both Golang and Python. I enjoy Golang quite a bit for it’s speed and the ability to compile and run a binary on just about any platform.
